attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Treasure III

data.description: Welcome to Plantation Estates!! A well-established community tucked away outside of city limits but close to schools, shopping, restaurants, military bases, beaches and much more! This beautiful 4 bed/4 bath home rests on 5 acres giving a sense of country living while still being on the coast! Upon arriving, you are welcomed by a generously spacious front yard with mature landscaping that includes magnolia and crepe myrtle trees that line the drive. When approaching the home,  you are greeted by a spacious front porch (sunrise/front). Entering the home boasts a vaulted foyer with a stairway leading to the second lvl, guest room to the right with full bath adjoining to foyer and entry access to the formal dining area and main living space. Check out the spacious living area that features TONS of natural lighting, cathedral ceilings, gas log fireplace, custom built-ins with natural hardwood floors and french door access to the back porch. Off of the main living area is the Primary Suite! This space is sure to please with natural lighting from the french door access and transom windows and newer LVP flooring. The primary bath includes a walk-in closet, spacious jetted soaking tub, two separate vanity sinks and separate shower. Across the living area is the beautiful chef's kitchen that is open. This space boasts tons of cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, water softener, pantry, kitchen island, formica counters and recess lighting to enhance the space. You also have access to the formal dining, breakfast nook with bow window, stairs to the 2nd lvl bonus and Laundry room(equipped with sink) with entry to 2 car garage. There are two separate sets of stairs leading to the 2nd lvl. From foyer upstairs, each spacious guest room features a full bath and you also have access to the HUGE bonus room. Home also features a full size back porch (sunset/back) with a beautiful view of the acreage. This acreage ALSO boasts horse pastures, corral and 49 x 50 workshop equipped with two working horse stables. Bring your horses!!! Split-rail fencing separates the acreage for multi-purpose use. This beautiful brick home also includes an energy efficient Geo-thermal HVAC system installed in 2019, water pump for property well installed in 2022, water softener and gas logs installed in 2022. You DON'T want to miss out on this one!
